<h2>_("Welcome to Blue Fruit!")</h2>
<p>Blue Fruit is a central list of download links of <a href="https://cwpat.me/fangames-intro/">IWBTG fangames</a>. It replaces the <a href="https://www21.atwiki.jp/iwannabethewiki/pages/283.html">Aiwana wiki</a>.
<br/><br/>
When games are approved by the review process here, they will be added automatically to <a href="https://delicious-fruit.com/">Delicious Fruit</a>, the fangame review site.
<br/><br/>
Click the links in the top right to change between the English and Japanese translations of the site.
</p>

